<div class="flex flex-col justify-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl">
    <h2 class="mt-6 text-center text-3xl leading-9 font-extrabold text-gray-900">
      About Us
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-8 text-center text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      Launched in May 2020 by a group of University of Georgia Students in response
      to local nonprofits’ increased need for volunteers as they build up capacity
      to support the community during COVID-19 and the ongoing economic crisis,
      <%= CITY_NAME %> Help With COVID is a partnership platform where nonprofits can
      efficiently recruit volunteers in the Greater <%= CITY_NAME %> area for in-person
      <u>and</u> remote opportunities.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-center text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      If you are a <%= CITY_NAME %> nonprofit interested in learning more about
      how our platform can best support you, contact us at
      <%= mail_to AFFILIATE_EMAIL, nil, target: '_blank', class: 'text-' + @primary_color + '-500' %>.
      We send out regular newsletters to our volunteers about the latest opportunities,
      and our team is happy to provide custom support for your organization—from
      posting opportunities and collecting applications to targeted recruiting.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-center text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      We believe good tools should be shared. In fact, <%= CITY_NAME %> Help With COVID was made possible by our friends
      at <a href="http://www.newhavenhelpwithcovid.com/" class="text-<%=PRIMARY_COLOR %>-500">New Haven Help With COVID</a>. If you are currently outside of <%= CITY_NAME %> and think that your
      local community could use a partnership platform like ours, reach out to us at
      <%= mail_to AFFILIATE_EMAIL, nil, target: '_blank', class: 'text-' + @primary_color + '-500' %> or
      our affiliates at <%= mail_to 'newhavenpandemic@gmail.com', nil, target: '_blank', class: 'text-' + @primary_color + '-500' %>.
      We are happy to discuss about sharing code and best practices.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 mb-4 text-center text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      Credits to
      <%= link_to 'HelpWithCovid.com', 'https://helpwithcovid.com/', target: '_blank', class: 'text-' + @primary_color + '-500' %>
      for the general template for this website.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col mt-8">
    <div class="-my-2 py-2 overflow-x-auto sm:-mx-6 sm:px-6 lg:-mx-8 lg:px-8">
      <div class="align-middle inline-block min-w-full shadow overflow-hidden sm:rounded-lg border-b border-gray-200">
        <table class="min-w-full">
          <tbody>
          <% striped_classes_cycle = [ "bg-white", "bg-gray-50" ] %>
          <% DEVS.each do |group, devs| %>
            <% if !group.empty? %>
              <tr class="<%= cycle striped_classes_cycle %>">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-no-wrap text-sm leading-5 font-medium text-white text-center bg-<%= PRIMARY_COLOR %>-500">
                  <%= html_escape group %>
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-no-wrap text-sm leading-5 text-gray-500 text-center bg-<%= PRIMARY_COLOR %>-500">
                </td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>
            <% devs.each do |name, role| %>
              <tr class="<%= cycle striped_classes_cycle %>">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-no-wrap text-sm leading-5 font-medium text-gray-900 text-center">
                  <%= html_escape name %>
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-no-wrap text-sm leading-5 text-gray-500 text-center">
                  <%= html_escape role %>
                </td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>
          <% end %>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sm:mx-auto sm:w-full sm:max-w-lg">
    <h2 class="mt-8 text-center text-3xl leading-9 font-extrabold text-gray-900">
      Thank you to all volunteers!
    </h2>
  </div>
</div>
